HEADWORD: Bird pepper
<hw>Bird" pep`per</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A species of capsicum
(<spn>Capsicum baccatum</spn>), whose small, conical, coral-red fruit is
among the most piquant of all red peppers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

